<h1>Learn More About: </h1>
<h3> <%= @all_actors %> Actors: </h3>
<% @actors.each do |actor| %>
   <li> <%= link_to actor.name, actor_path(actor) %> </li>
    <% end %> <br>
    <p> The actor who participated in the most events is <%= link_to @most_events.name, actor_path(@most_events) %>, who participated in <%= @most_events.events.count %> events. <p> 
<br> 
<h3> <%= @total_moments %> Moments: </h3>
<% @moments.each do |moment| %>
    <li> <%= link_to moment.name, historical_moment_path(moment) %> </li>
     <% end %> <br>
<p> The Historical Moment with the most events is <%= link_to @hm_most_events.name, historical_moment_path(@hm_most_events) %>, with <%= @hm_most_events.events.count %> events. <p> 
<p> The Historical Moment with the most actors is <%= link_to @hm_most_actors.name, historical_moment_path(@hm_most_actors) %>, with <%= @hm_most_events.actors.count %> actors. <p>
<p> The Historical Moment with the most documents is <%= link_to @hm_most_docs.name, historical_moment_path(@hm_most_docs) %>, with <%= @hm_most_docs.documents.count %> documents. <p>